From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: aaa aaa <aaaaaaa@aaa.edu.cn>
Date: Wed, 3 Dec 2026 20:03:22 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] board: rockchip: add HINLINK H29K

The HINLINK H29K is a single board computer based on the
RK3528 SoC. Add support for the HINLINK H29K board.

Signed-off-by: aaa aaa <aaaaaaa@aaa.edu.cn>
---
 configs/hinlink-h29k-rk3528_defconfig           | 721 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dts/upstream/src/arm64/rockchip/rk3528-hinlink-h29k.dts | 502 +++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 1223 insertions(+)

--- /dev/null
+++ b/configs/hinlink-h29k-rk3528_defconfig
